🔐 Project Overview
The Password Manager is a CRUD-based web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to securely manage website credentials using browser localStorage.

This project focuses on DOM manipulation, CRUD operations, localStorage, search functionality, clipboard interaction, and responsive UI development.

✨ Features
Add password
Edit password
Delete password
Copy password
Search by website
Password strength indicator
Show/Hide password
Save data in localStorage
Responsive UI

🛠 Technologies Used
